This project demonstrates how to use my Django template tag to improve the way you can display user feedback messages from the Messages Framework in Django 1.2.

To get going...
git clone git://github.com/mrben/nicer_django_messages_output.git
cd nicer_django_messages_output
python manage.py syncdb

Feel free to user any of it, however you want. This work is in the public domain. http://creativecommons.org/licenses/publicdomain/